Also, the Quest Pro is not
that comfortable anyway.

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:04.680
But the point is this,
for Apple, made the choice

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:09.000
of taking the battery off of
the headset, which means okay,

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.380
now there's nothing on
the back of your head,

00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:12.540
so you can wear it and
lean up against things,

00:04:12.540 --> 00:04:14.220
and that might be an upside,

00:04:14.220 --> 00:04:16.110
but that also now means you have to deal

00:04:16.110 --> 00:04:19.290
with this cable all the time
running up to your head,

00:04:19.290 --> 00:04:22.380
and the fact that it's
very front weighted now.

00:04:22.380 --> 00:04:24.360
All of the weight is on
the front of your face.

